(148, 52, 3, 'Filling in the daily diary', 'Filling in the daily diary', 'Filling in the daily diary', 'We would like you to put information about your medication, wellbeing and where you have been driving throughout the day, into a diary. This will help us to see how your medication, wellbeing and location might influence your wheelchair driving. In the first instance, this diary will be paper based. Later in the trial, an electronic tablet may be added to your chair, so that the information could be added electronically via a touch screen. If a Tablet is provided would you be able to use a touchscreen to enter data? Alternatively, your carer may be able to help with entering this information.', 'We would like you to put information about your medication, wellbeing and where you have been driving throughout the day, into a diary. This will help us to see how your medication, wellbeing and location might influence your wheelchair driving. In the first instance, this diary will be paper based. Later in the trial, an electronic tablet may be added to your chair, so that the information could be added electronically via a touch screen. If a Tablet is provided would you be able to use a touchscreen to enter data? Alternatively, your carer may be able to help with entering this information.', 'We would like you to put information about your medication, wellbeing and where you have been driving throughout the day, into a diary. This will help us to see how your medication, wellbeing and location might influence your wheelchair driving. In the first instance, this diary will be paper based. Later in the trial, an electronic tablet may be added to your chair, so that the information could be added electronically via a touch screen. If a Tablet is provided would you be able to use a touchscreen to enter data? Alternatively, your carer may be able to help with entering this information.', 13, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
